*Pozdrav* nam je stigao preko društvenih mreža. (We got a greeting through social networks.)

Nismo čuli *pozdrav*, već tražili odgovor. (We didn't hear a greeting, we were looking for an answer.)

Oni su nam uputili iskrene *pozdrave*. (They sent us sincere greetings.)

Ona je odgovorila na naš *pozdrav*. (She responded to our greeting.)

Učenik je zaboravio da izgovori *pozdrav*. (The student forgot to say the greeting.)

Svi su se obradovali *pozdravu*. (Everyone was delighted with the greeting.)